H.B. 1106
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
Apr 29, 2026
SESSION 2025
HOUSE PRINCIPAL CLERK
H D
HOUSE BILL DRH10621-LUa-148B
Short Title: NC Pre-K Funding/Iredell County. (Public)
Sponsors: Representative McNeely.
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE NC PREKINDERGARTEN (NC PRE-K) FUNDS FOR
3 IREDELL COUNTY PARTNERSHIP FOR YOUNG CHILDREN, INC.
4 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
5 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to Iredell County
6 Partnership for Young Children, Inc., the sum of two hundred sixty thousand five hundred
7 thirty-eight dollars ($260,538) in recurring funds beginning in the 2026-2027 fiscal year for the
8 NC Prekindergarten (NC Pre-K) program in Iredell County. These funds will provide Iredell
9 County with the same funding level per child as Beaufort County.
10 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2026.
*DRH10621-LUa-148B*

